NAME
	wiz_dir - return a wizards work path

SYNOPSIS
	string wiz_dir()

DESCRIPTION
	Returns the path to a wizards work directory.

RETURN VALUE
	A string containing the path to the wizards directory.

SEE ALSO
	afun/absolute_path, afun/base_name, afun/clone_num, afun/file_name, 
	afun/path_file, kfun/find_object, kfun/object_name
